Comment.val: /* Dit programma zorgt voor de splitsing van het batchproces Aanmaken revisievoorstellen. programma wordt vanuit het programma er onder aangeroepen.*/

Text.val: Parameters uit dit programma gelijk houden aan programma

SQL_STMT_U.val: select count(*) from :1 w inner join :2 ppr on to_char(ppr.ppr_relatienummer) = w.wk_categorie_1 inner join :3 p on p.pr_productnummer = ppr.ppr_productnummer inner join :4 c on c.cl_nummer = ppr.ppr_relatienummer left outer join :5 o1 on o1.onld_relatienummer = ppr.ppr_relatienummer and o1.onld_klasse = 32 and o1.onld_productnummer = ppr.ppr_productnummer and o1.onld_product_volgnummer = ppr.ppr_volgnr_per_product inner join :5 o2 on o2.onld_relatienummer = ppr.ppr_relatienummer and o2.onld_klasse = 31 and o2.onld_productnummer = ppr.ppr_productnummer and o2.onld_product_volgnummer = ppr.ppr_volgnr_per_product where w.wk_terminal = ~6 and w.wk_soort = 'REVR' and ppr.ppr_productnummer between ~7 and ~8 and ((~9 <> 0 and ppr.ppr_volgnr_per_product = ~9) or ~9 = 0) and p.pr_rev_bgopdr_gebruiken = 2 and (((~11 = 1 and ~13 = 0) and (p.pr_check_accrd_rebal_voorstel = 0 or (ppr.ppr_rebal_voorstel_accoord >= ppr.ppr_rebal_voorstel_verstuurd and ppr.ppr_rebal_voorstel_verstuurd <> '00000000'))) or not (~11 = 1 and ~13 = 0)) and (~11 = 0 or p.pr_bgs_methode_rebalance <> 3) and ((~15 <> 0 and o1.onld_id_nummer between ~14 and ~15) or (~14=0 and o1.onld_id_nummer is null) or ~15 = 0) and ((~17 <> 0 and o2.onld_id_nummer between ~16 and ~17) or ~17 = 0) and ((~12 <> 0 and o2.onld_limiet between ~10 and ~12) or ~12 = 0)

select min(relatie), max(relatie) from (select NTILE(:10) over(order by relatie asc) groep, relatie from (select relatie from (select ppr.ppr_relatienummer relatie from :1 w inner join :2 ppr on to_char(ppr.ppr_relatienummer)= w.wk_categorie_1 inner join :3 p on p.pr_productnummer=ppr.ppr_productnummer inner join :4 c on c.cl_nummer=ppr.ppr_relatienummer left outer join :5 o1 on o1.onld_relatienummer=ppr.ppr_relatienummer and o1.onld_klasse=32 and o1.onld_productnummer=ppr.ppr_productnummer and o1.onld_product_volgnummer=ppr.ppr_volgnr_per_product inner join :5 o2 on o2.onld_relatienummer=ppr.ppr_relatienummer and o2.onld_klasse=31 and o2.onld_productnummer=ppr.ppr_productnummer and o2.onld_product_volgnummer=ppr.ppr_volgnr_per_product where w.wk_terminal=~6 and w.wk_soort='REVR' and ppr.ppr_productnummer between ~7 and ~8 and ((~9<>0 and ppr.ppr_volgnr_per_product = ~9) or ~9=0) and p.pr_rev_bgopdr_gebruiken = 2 and (((~11=1 and ~13=0) and(p.pr_check_accrd_rebal_voorstel=0 or (ppr.ppr_rebal_voorstel_accoord>=ppr.ppr_rebal_voorstel_verstuurd and ppr.ppr_rebal_voorstel_verstuurd<>'00000000')))or not(~11=1 and ~13=0)) and (~11=0 or p.pr_bgs_methode_rebalance<>3) and ((~15<>0 and o1.onld_id_nummer between ~14 and ~15) or (~14=0 and o1.onld_id_nummer is null) or ~15=0) and ((~17<>0 and o2.onld_id_nummer between ~16 and ~17) or ~17=0) and ((~12<>0 and o2.onld_limiet between ~18 and ~12) or ~12=0) ) order by relatie)) group by groep order by groep

select count(*) from :2 ppr inner join :3 p on p.pr_productnummer = ppr.ppr_productnummer inner join :4 c on c.cl_nummer = ppr.ppr_relatienummer left outer join :5 o1 on o1.onld_relatienummer = ppr.ppr_relatienummer and o1.onld_klasse = 32 and o1.onld_productnummer = ppr.ppr_productnummer and o1.onld_product_volgnummer = ppr.ppr_volgnr_per_product inner join :5 o2 on o2.onld_relatienummer = ppr.ppr_relatienummer and o2.onld_klasse = 31 and o2.onld_productnummer = ppr.ppr_productnummer and o2.onld_product_volgnummer = ppr.ppr_volgnr_per_product where ppr.ppr_relatienummer between ~19 and ~20 and ppr.ppr_productnummer between ~7 and ~8 and ((~9 <> 0 and ppr.ppr_volgnr_per_product = ~9) or ~9 = 0) and p.pr_rev_bgopdr_gebruiken = 2 and (((~11 = 1 and ~13 = 0) and (p.pr_check_accrd_rebal_voorstel = 0 or (ppr.ppr_rebal_voorstel_accoord >= ppr.ppr_rebal_voorstel_verstuurd and ppr.ppr_rebal_voorstel_verstuurd <> '00000000'))) or not (~11 = 1 and ~10 = 0)) and (~11 = 0 or p.pr_bgs_methode_rebalance <> 3) and ((~15 <> 0 and o1.onld_id_nummer between ~14 and ~15) or (~14=0 and o1.onld_id_nummer is null) or ~15 = 0) and ((~17 <> 0 and o2.onld_id_nummer between ~16 and ~17) or ~17 = 0) and ((~13 <> 0 and o2.onld_limiet between ~18 and ~13) or ~13 = 0) and ( :1 <> 3 or c.cl_clientgroep in (select cgv.cgv_clientgroep from :6 cgv where cgv.cgv_adviseur = :12 ))

select min(relatie), max(relatie) from (select NTILE(:1) over(order by relatie asc) groep, relatie from (select relatie from (select ppr.ppr_relatienummer relatie from :2 ppr inner join :3 p on p.pr_productnummer = ppr.ppr_productnummer inner join :4 c on c.cl_nummer = ppr.ppr_relatienummer left outer join :5 o1 on o1.onld_relatienummer = ppr.ppr_relatienummer and o1.onld_klasse = 32 and o1.onld_productnummer = ppr.ppr_productnummer and o1.onld_product_volgnummer = ppr.ppr_volgnr_per_product inner join :5 o2 on o2.onld_relatienummer = ppr.ppr_relatienummer and o2.onld_klasse = 31 and o2.onld_productnummer = ppr.ppr_productnummer and o2.onld_product_volgnummer = ppr.ppr_volgnr_per_product where ppr.ppr_relatienummer between ~20 and ~21 and ppr.ppr_productnummer between ~7 and ~8 and ((~9 <> 0 and ppr.ppr_volgnr_per_product = ~9) or ~9 = 0) and p.pr_rev_bgopdr_gebruiken = 2 and (((~11 = 1 and ~13 = 0) and (p.pr_check_accrd_rebal_voorstel = 0 or (ppr.ppr_rebal_voorstel_accoord >= ppr.ppr_rebal_voorstel_verstuurd and ppr.ppr_rebal_voorstel_verstuurd <> '00000000'))) or not (~11 = 1 and ~13 = 0)) and (~11 = 0 or p.pr_bgs_methode_rebalance <> 3) and ((~15 <> 0 and o1.onld_id_nummer between ~14 and ~15) or (~14=0 and o1.onld_id_nummer is null) or ~15 = 0) and ((~17 <> 0 and o2.onld_id_nummer between ~16 and ~17) or ~17 = 0) and ((~19 <> 0 and o2.onld_limiet between ~18 and ~19) or ~19 = 0) and ( :12 <> 3 or c.cl_clientgroep in ( select cgv.cgv_clientgroep from :6 cgv where cgv.cgv_adviseur = :10 )) ) order by relatie)) group by groep order by groep
